Package com.intellij.psi.codeStyle

Class LegacyCodeStyleSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.psi.codeStyle.CommonCodeStyleSettings
      • com.intellij.psi.codeStyle.LegacyCodeStyleSettings
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CodeStyleSettings

    public class LegacyCodeStyleSettings
extends CommonCodeStyleSettings
    Contains fields which are left for compatibility with earlier versions. These fields shouldn't be used anymore. Every language must have its own settings which can be retrieved using CodeStyleSettings.getCommonSettings(Language) or CodeStyle.getLanguageSettings(PsiFile).
    See Also:
    LanguageCodeStyleSettingsProvider
